    \vspace{-1.5ex}

    \rule{\textwidth}{0.5\fboxrule}

      \textbf{Parameters}
      \vspace{-1ex}

      \begin{quote}
        \begin{Ventry}{xxxx}

          \item[room]

          Room where is the system that we want to evaluate.

            {\it (type=Object of the class Room.)}

        \end{Ventry}

      \end{quote}

      \textbf{Return Value}
    \vspace{-1ex}

      {\it (type=Integer.)}

      \end{quote}
